name: EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryBrowserState
desc: The possible states of an accessory browser.

items.name: case wiFiUnavailable
items.desc: Wi-Fi is unavailable, typically because the user has placed the device in Airplane Mode or explicitly turned off Wi-Fi.

items.name: case stopped
items.desc: The browser is not actively searching for unconfigured accessories.

items.name: case searching
items.desc: The browser is actively searching for unconfigured accessory.

items.name: case configuring
items.desc: The browser is actively configuring an accessory.
